{"tid":2058662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉爆樽扑女警 沙展押後答辯","createTime":"2020-06-10T10:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T12:41:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1fa0b5d48bff0ce6d033e5f5186d7ea4ec3548f5","tid":2058662,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200610/HOVFJ2IXJJ3VUEHM2SSWZW5DEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200610%2FHOVFJ2IXJJ3VUEHM2SSWZW5DEM%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=7d13e0d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200610%2FHOVFJ2IXJJ3VUEHM2SSWZW5DEM%2F&h=fa431911\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200610/HOVFJ2IXJJ3VUEHM2SSWZW5DEM/</a><br />\n<br />\n涉爆樽扑女警 沙展押後答辯<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】天水圍警署十名警務人員4月下班食消夜時，一名警長涉嫌向女警「爆樽」，用玻璃樽擊傷女警頭部，事後逃離現場。警長及後被捕，重案組落案控告他一項普通襲擊罪，案件昨提堂。警長續准保釋候訊，其間不得接觸當晚在場的同袍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HVIEIAL2RBLFPEE7WYCAKKIXHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHVIEIAL2RBLFPEE7WYCAKKIXHY.jpg&h=56415e63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（已節錄）<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC926/20<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪"},{"pid":"862307ceb4638d1fd0026d5c22b893c693d3d4e3","tid":2058662,"uid":201604,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:31:57.000Z","msg":"女警狗就係用黎畀男警狗扑架啦"},{"pid":"48bd024d92304ea1431d9ff1624283d8ce805aee","tid":2058662,"uid":3457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:34:04.000Z","msg":"唔係暴動咩？ 爆樽wo <br />\n人地行下街都暴動 反而爆樽唔洗"},{"pid":"eb5e9216c0332f5cda5674fe414d966fa4613974","tid":2058662,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:37:52.000Z","msg":"無狗閪圖，好難判斷抵唔抵扑<img src=